gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model

Class DisplayNameComparator

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.va.med.srcalc.domain.model.DisplayNameComparator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.util.Comparator<Variable>

    public final class DisplayNameComparator
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Comparator<Variable>

    Compares Variables (case-insensitively) by their display names. In order to be consistent with equals, if the display names compare as equal, then this order compares the variable keys.

    This comparison is consistent with equals: compare(Variable, Variable) returns 0 if and only if the variables are considered equal.
